I replaced mine a while back:
http://guacamolebus.blogspot.com/2009/02/turn-signal-switch-replacement.html

I've found that if the switch isn't broken, and it doesn't return, the
steering wheel is misaligned, or the alignment is off (the steering
wheel adjusted to look straight.).

